## Usage ä½¿ç”¨

```shell
pip install -U flomo
```

```python
from flomo import Flomo, Parser
authorization = "Bearer xxxxxxxxxxx"
flomo = Flomo(authorization)
memos = flomo.get_all_memos()

memo = Parser(memos[-1])
print(memo.text) # memo çº¯æ–‡æœ¬
print(memo.url)  # memo é“¾æ¥
print(memo.tags)
```

